BBQ Sauce

Saut\'e onion and garlic in oil.
&
1 medium onion, chopped
2 cloves garlic, minced
1/3 cup oil
&&&

Add ingredients.
&
2 1/2 cups tomato sauce
1/4 cup water
1 cup brown sugar
1 Tbsp molasses
1/2 cup mustard
1 Tbsp salt
1 tsp allspice
1 Tbsp crushed red pepper
1 sprig parsely
&&&

Bring to a boil, simmer for an hour.
&&&

Add lemon juice and soy sauce and cook for 10-15 minutes more.
&
3/4 cup lemon juice
2 Tbsp soy sauce
&&&
